name: Phi Barrier Film Holder
short_description: Phi Barrier Film Holder is a durable film dispenser, protecting the barrier sheets roll and making it easier to use.
long_description: Very simple and effortless to use and easy to open for replacing barrier films. Hard quality transparent plastic makes it easier to track the inserted film and to spot when it needs replacement. Easily fits in every surrounding and makes your work more organized and hygienic.Â NOTE: The holder does not come with a barrier film inserted.
